{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Krzk9umHjbmJhuv7wji9Mo","type":"tool_result","content":"@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/components/WheelVisualization.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   360:6  warning  React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'getWinnerScrollPosition' and 'scrollPosition'. Either include them or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/context/LordOfRngsContext.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   161:6  warning  React Hook useEffect has missing dependencies: 'activeRound' and 'address'. Either include them or remove the dependency array  react-hooks/exhaustive-deps\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/player-profile/components/PlayerAvatar.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   41:3  warning  Unused eslint-disable directive (no problems were reported from '@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars')\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CryptoCrashPage.tsx\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   51:9  warning  Unexpected console statement. Only these console methods are allowed: warn, error  no-console\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: ✖ 10 problems (0 errors, 10 warnings)\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint:   0 errors and 1 warning potentially fixable with the `--fix` option.\n@rng-utopia/platform:lint: \n\n Tasks:    17 successful, 17 total\nCached:    16 cached, 17 total\n  Time:    9.923s","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1e81398f-978c-4fff-848f-a37f36dac162","uuid":"0cad3c57-752a-4968-a5f2-65bb97c618b0","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"@rng-utopia/platform:lint: /workspaces/rng-utopia/so